rows.label: qev091702_MSG0001
rows.name: Last I checked, you still hadn't finished the job. Scared?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0039
rows.name: Persist

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0040
rows.name: Exclaim that you'll never give up.

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0041
rows.name: Concede

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0042
rows.name: Say that the contest is just too hard.

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0002
rows.name:
Stubborn, aren't you?
Well, if you change your mind, just let me know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0003
rows.name: Giving up, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0004
rows.name:
You sure?
That means I get a hundred grand from the Murderess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0043
rows.name: Retract

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0044
rows.name: Tell Yolanda you were only kidding.

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0045
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0046
rows.name: Give up for sure.

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0005
rows.name: Suuuure you were.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0005_2
rows.name: Look, I wouldn't joke about this if I were you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0006
rows.name:
The Murderess looked like she was
about to kill you a second ago.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0007
rows.name: Yeeees! Payday for ME![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0008
rows.name: Thanks for being spineless.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0009
rows.name:
Man, it feels GOOD to soak the Murderess
for a fat stack of cash.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0010
rows.name: Yeah, yeah. Laugh it up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0011
rows.name:
Just watch your back the next time
we're on a mission together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0012
rows.name: That'd be funnier if your stare wasn't so piercing...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0013
rows.name: Damn. You did it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0014
rows.name: Time to pony up the cash, loser![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0015
rows.name: Fine. Here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0016
rows.name:
Wait, this is it? Ten credits?!
Are you kidding me right now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0017
rows.name:
We figured you were stubborn enough to win somehow,
so betting was...subdued.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0018
rows.name:
That's a total crock. I know you'd have
put in at least two thousand credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0019
rows.name: Ugh... I hate that you know that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0020
rows.name: Fine again! The pot was 2,101 credits. Here you go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_JNK0050
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev091702_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask the Murderess for your share of the pot.

rows.label: qev091702_JNK0060
rows.name: Celebrate

rows.label: qev091702_SEL0061
rows.name: Suggest moving the party over to the diner.

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0021
rows.name:
You didn't bet, sweetie.
If you want a payout, put some skin in the game.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0022
rows.name:
Damn, that's cold.
You could at least cough up a few bones.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0023
rows.name: I'm not parting with a single credit![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0024
rows.name:
Now you're talkin'.
Let's kick back a few rounds to finish off the day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0025
rows.name: If you think I'm buying, you better start making other plans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0026
rows.name: Geez, you're cheap.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0027
rows.name: Flattery will get you nowhere, my dear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0028
rows.name: You hear about that job with the huge reward?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0029
rows.name: Ooh, you're speaking my language. Do tell.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0030
rows.name: Ugh, not the Murderess...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0031
rows.name: Spill it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0032
rows.name: Well, I couldn't get many details from Mission Control...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0033
rows.name: But I think it's a bounty on some xeno.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0034
rows.name: Alien hunting, huh? Sounds like a hoot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0035
rows.name: Eleonora's our best bet for info. Let's hit her up ASAP.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0036
rows.name: And don't none of you even THINK about taking this job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0037
rows.name:
I'm already killing one mark here,
but I'd be happy to make it two.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0038
rows.name: Eeep![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0047
rows.name: That idiot! Could his timing have BEEN any worse?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091702_MSG0048
rows.name:
Mentioning a high-paying job around the Murderess is
like spreading your picnic out in front of a half-starved
hyena![ST:wait ]
